snippet.title: Celebrities Speaks On Amber Heard Manipulating Her Way to Success
snippet.description:
Celebrities Speaks On Amber Heard Manipulating Her Way to Success
Johnny Depp's attorneys told the Court of Appeal that Amber Heard's statement that she contributed her $7 million divorce settlement to charity was a "calculated and manipulative lie." The Hollywood actor is seeking the Court of Appeal to compel a retrial of his defamation lawsuit against The Sun after a scathing High Court decision that he attacked his ex-wife and left her in fear for her life
